title: A tale of two continents
description:
There is news in the world of tea, news big enough for the big papers.  My movie is an epic tale that will take us from the terraced hillsides of 3000 BC china to the box of tea in your kitchen cupboard, this very day.

We are going to change the world, one cup at a time.

Kind regards,
Monkey


"Film? What film?" - Monkey&#039;s nan
